<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Morris Clay</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,300;0,6..72,400;0,6..72,500;1,6..72,300;1,6..72,400;1,6..72,500&family=JetBrains+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --ink: #2b2926;
  --ink-soft: #3d3a36;
  --paper: #f0ece4;
  --paper-deep: #e6e1d7;
  --faded: #918a7e;
  --rule: #cdc6b8;
  --accent: #5c7c5a;
  --accent-deep: #4a6548;
  --accent-light: rgba(92, 124, 90, 0.08);
}

*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html {
  font-size: 18px;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ink);
  background: var(--paper);
  line-height: 1.72;
  letter-spacing: 0.004em;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.container {
  max-width: 32em;
  text-align: center;
}

h1 {
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

.tagline {
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--faded);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.bio {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  text-align: left;
}

.bio p {
  margin-bottom: 1em;
}

.bio p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.links {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1.5em;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.links a {
  color: var(--faded);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
  padding: 0.5em 0;
}

.links a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-deep);
}

.divider {
  width: 24px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}

.writing-section {
  margin-top: 4rem;
  padding-top: 2rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  width: 100%;
}

.writing-section h2 {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faded);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.writing-list {
  list-style: none;
  text-align: left;
}

.writing-list li {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.writing-list a {
  color: var(--ink);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 400;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.writing-list a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-deep);
}

.writing-list .date {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--faded);
  margin-left: 0.8em;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

::selection {
  background: rgba(92, 124, 90, 0.16);
  color: inherit;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  html { font-size: 16px; }
  body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .links { gap: 1em; font-size: 0.6rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Morris Clay</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Deep tech investor</p>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>I invest in deep tech at the earliest stages, working with founders on the hardest question their company faces: <em>what shape should this thing take?</em></p>
    <p>I help widen the aperture. Then the founder drives.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="links">
    <a href="mailto:morris@lunarventures.eu">Email</a>
    <span class="divider"></span>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/morris-clay/">LinkedIn</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="writing-section">
    <h2>Writing</h2>
    <ul class="writing-list">
      <li>
        <a href="/blog/the-shape-of-the-thing">The Shape of the Thing</a>
        <span class="date">Feb 2026</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
